  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595495630143-NS5TTWUQZ6UV50W5QVDI/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Last week while I was up in San Francisco for a quick day trip, I was able to check out the new <a href=\"http://www.colorfactory.co/\">Color Factory</a> and it was AMAZING. It just opened today and I highly recommend you go and reserve tickets! I took my friend Pamelyn from <a href=\"https://www.basheryandco.com/\">Bashery &amp; Co</a> and met up with <a href=\"http://instagram.com/alishylishy\">Alisha</a> and some friends for the fun.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0b-.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595495677616-9K8M510N4X6RDLGW0EWI/0b-.jpeg\">\n</img></a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0c-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595495679870-83302ITX2ESZ88U2PAST/0c-Color%2BFactory%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0d-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595495680122-6EMWYAOEQ7YG5AL5EOBK/0d-Color%2BFactory%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0e-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595495682432-ZFCLJF0LCRCKA12X3401/0e-Color%2BFactory%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0f-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595495681733-9C0DNF41MXJWCCKDFELP/0f-Color%2BFactory%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0g-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595495685398-E9ZLY3GZOR2VY4JYXGA1/0g-Color%2BFactory%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0h-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595495690136-BKWEUHM6WHSNOZGTCCDL/0h-Color%2BFactory%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0i-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595495690503-4Q3LA0PRYVK25H2LR29J/0i-Color%2BFactory%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0j-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595495693194-0I3W49SEF9PS50P38D70/0j-Color%2BFactory%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0k-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595495696987-IPA9G42YICQ9WG5BEBWI/0k-Color%2BFactory%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0l-Color+Factory+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595495694938-SN2P3VF999V46GB321QS/0l-Color%2BFactory%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0m-14.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595495696463-6RTT4YXY8513M4L59O0X/0m-14.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n<a>\n<img alt=\"0n-15.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595495704942-TN2VCN3S9MY5M3RR9Z1K/0n-15.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>I had to<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vUSyqPgdWGA\"> vlog the experience</a>, as it was everything you would imagine it to be and more.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Photos by <a href=\"http://lishcreative.com/\">LISH Creative</a> - You can see Alisha's post <a href=\"http://lishcreative.com/blog/2017/7/28/inside-the-color-factory-in-san-francisco\">here</a>, which includes a fun video. We are already planning a trip back as there is a map we picked up at the end that shows 17 other activations throughout the city, including colorful murals that will only be up for a limited amount of time!</p><p>There are a couple sneak peeks at the next <a href=\"https://shop.amytangerine.com/subscribe\">Fresh Squeezed Fashion Tees</a>, which will be available to subscribers on August 9 through Aug 14! </p><p>Also, I am SUPER EXCITED to share that I will be teaching in the UK for the first time in late October with <a href=\"http://birdsofafeather.uk.com/workshops\">Birds of a Feather at Chateau Impney!</a> It will be a really fun-filled weekend - come join us!</p>"
